{"tid":1828052,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★里昂2020年風水指數：【港股或一直旺到7月】","createTime":"2020-01-17T12:46:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T07:30:30.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bed15d2a8f3114c2eaa256d0c66f2c55e40f4ce8","tid":1828052,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T12:46:05.000Z","msg":"中信里昂證券就發表了最新2020年風水指數，指今年為金鼠年，鼠作為「一家之主、群雄之首」，其八字與屬土雞的恒指和諧相處，料對恒指是「大吉」之兆。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【港股或一直旺到7月】</span><br />\n該行預測，今年農曆新年後港股開局不錯，料年初將會有一系列政策出台改善營商條件，並可靜待5至7月夏初的升勢。至於8至10月夏末，港股或出現獲利回吐，其中金融及銀行業表現較遜色；科技、電訊及公用事業則有望於10月及11月錄得不錯的升幅。至於年底將是旅遊及賭業的旺季。總括而言，今年全年港股走勢為「靠穩向上」，8至9月為全年高位。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200117/bkn-20200117153309030-0117_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200117%2Fbkn-20200117153309030-0117_00842_001.html&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKAEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=097f561c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200117/bkn-20200117153309030-0117_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"2814c60f03e68fd5c15ac631d0702011b25f3ff7","tid":1828052,"uid":82746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T12:46:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QxshhCE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQxshhCE.jpg&h=f2dca26c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53f08850d4d3687791b428bc4a63afbb6e32a47d","tid":1828052,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T12:46:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d85ebcd3751ee5f2a3b165bf3f2c08bb14cae07","tid":1828052,"u